    <gatha type="last">Catukkapañcakajjhānaṃ, katvā vikkhepanissaṭā.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1068"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Supakkhālitupaklesā , santacittā samāhitā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Pavivekarasassādaṃ, anubhonti yathāsukhaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1069"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Asubhaṃ  pana bhāvento, nimittaṃ yattha katthaci;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Uddhumātādibhedamhi, uggaṇheyyāsubhe kathaṃ?</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1070"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Ekāhādimatikkantaṃ, uddhumātakamīritaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vigatacchavi bībhacchaṃ, nīlākāraṃ vinīlakaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1071"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vikiṇṇapubbakudhitaṃ, paribhinnaṃ vipubbakaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Viccheditaṅgapaccaṅgaṃ, vicchiddakaṃ kaḷevaraṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1072"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vividhākārapāṇehi, khajjamānaṃ vikhāditaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vināsitaṅgapaccaṅgaṃ, vikkhittanti pavuccati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1073"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Pādādibhaṅgavikkhittaṃ, hatavikkhittakaṃ mataṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Lohitaṃ lohitākiṇṇaṃ, puḷavaṃ kimisaṅkulaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1074"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Aṭṭhisaṅkhalikāmattaṃ, aṭṭhikanti ca sabbathā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Saṇṭhānākārabhedena, dasadhāsubhadesanā.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1075"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Tatthevaṃ dasadhā bhede, nijjīvakuṇapāsubhe;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Ujjhite bhūmibhāgasmiṃ, matakāye kaḷevare.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1076"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Labbhamānakamākāraṃ, oloketvā salakkhaṇaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Uggahetvāna cittena, taṃtaṃnāmena bhāvaye.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1077"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Paṭikūlañca jegucchaṃ, duggandhañca virūpakaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Harāyitamajaññañca, hīḷitaṃ vikkhitāsivaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1078"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Iccevamasubhākāre,</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Katvābhogaṃ tu yogino;</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Bhāventassupacāro ca,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Paṭibhāgo ca jāyati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1079"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Paṭibhāganimittaṃ  tu, upacārena sevato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Appeti paṭhamajjhāna-metthevaṃ samathe nayo.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1080"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vinā  saddhammaṃ panidaṃ, sarīraṃ bālananditaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vipattipariyosānaṃ, avassaṃ bhedagāmikaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1081"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Yathā idaṃ tathā etaṃ, yathā etaṃ tathā idaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Jīvamānañca nijjīvameva dhammaparāyaṇaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1082"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Sabhāvo sopi dehassa,</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Sabbassāpi ca sabbathā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Vicitabbā dhirenāpi,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Esāyaṃ niyatā gati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1083"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Aniccaṃ khayadhammañca, dukkhameva bhayāvahaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Anattā ca parābhūtā, vibbhijjati khaṇe khaṇe.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1084"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vināsamānassākāraṃ, tatthevaṃ pana passato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vipassanābhāvanāti, tamīrenti tathāgatā.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1085"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Bhāvanaṃ duvidhampetaṃ, bhāventi puna paṇḍitā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Jīvamānepi kāyamhi, taṃtadākārasambhave.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1086"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Jīvamānopi kāyoyaṃ,</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Kuṇapova sabhāvato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Tamalaṅkārapaṭicchanno,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Bālānaṃ na pakāsati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1087"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Bahi maṭṭhamupaṭṭhāti, anto kuṇapapūritaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Uggharantaṃ paggharantaṃ, navadvāramalassavaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1088"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Sarīraṃ niccaduggandhaṃ, nānākimisamākulaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Tacamaṃsapaṭicchannaṃ, aṭṭhipañjarasaṇṭhitaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1089"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vaccakūpamidaṃ  nāma, dvattiṃsāsucipūritaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Narānukkārabhūmīva, nekavassagaṇocitā.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1090"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Susānagamanosānaṃ, bahusādhāraṇāsubhaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Gaṇḍabhūtaṃ sallabhūtaṃ, bahudukkhanibandhanaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1091"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Nānābyādhisamākiṇṇaṃ , nānopaddavasaṃkulaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Nānānatthasamodhānaṃ, nānāsaṃklesavatthukaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1092"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Positampi ciraṃ kālaṃ, mamaṃkāramamāyitaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Lahudujjanamittova, pīḷitaṃ sampadussati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1093"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Parihāyati nissāraṃ, jaratāpi taṃ yobbanaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Maccubhajjitamaccanta-masesaṃ paribhijjati.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1094"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Tathāpi jālasantāno, bahusambhārasaṅkhato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vatthālaṅkārasañchanno, mālāgandhādisobhito.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1095"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Saviññattivikārehi, vicittākāramaṇḍito;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Kāyo līḷavilāsehi, palambheti mahājanaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1096"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Vañcitā yena dummedhā, kāmaklesamalīmayā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Pūrenti caturāpāyaṃ, māradheyyānusārino.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1097"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Evamādīnavaṃ ñatvā, pūtikāye vicakkhaṇā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Asubhādikamākāra-mārabbha chandupaṭṭhahuṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1098"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Yasmiṃ patanti kuṇape viparītasaññā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Saṃklesapāpavasagā visamaṃ carantā;</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Taṃ passathetamasubhampi vināsadhammaṃ,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Iccevamāha sugato dasadhā vibhāgaṃ.</gatha>
    <hangnum nr="1099"/>
    <gatha type="1"> Satthārā kasiṇañca yaṃ dasavidhaṃ vikkhepavikkhambhanaṃ,</gatha>
    <gatha type="2">Kāmaklesavināsanaṃ dasavidhaṃ yañcāsubhaṃ bhāsitaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="3">Dibbabrahmasukhāvahaṃ  samapadaṃ vijjodayaṃ yoginā,</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Kammaṭṭhānamalaṃ tamuttamaguṇenāsevitaṃ sevituṃ.</gatha>
    <centered>Iti nāmarūpaparicchede kasiṇāsubhavibhāgo nāma</centered>
    <centered>Aṭṭhamo paricchedo.</centered>
  </text>
